We're now testing this condition tries, so it is worth breaking it out into its own method:```
private boolean retriesLeft() {
  return retryCount <= maxRetryCount;
};```

In addition, rather than using a nested if, negate the above condition and make it the first branch if an if-else if-else sequence, that simply returns na.

